@startuml command-renderer-architecture
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam componentBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam componentBorderColor #888
skinparam packageBackgroundColor #F0F8FF

title Command-Based Renderer Architecture

package "Application Layer" #E8F4F8 {
    component [Application] as App
    
    component [Scene] as Scene
}

package "Renderer Core" #FFE8E8 {
    component [Renderer] as Renderer
    component [SwapChain] as SwapChain
    component [CommandRecorder] as CmdRec
}

package "Resource Management" #E8FFE8 {
    component [FrameManager] as FrameMgr
    component [CommandPool] as CmdPool
    component [RenderTarget] as RT
    component [ResourceManager] as ResMgr
}

package "GPU Backend" #E8E8FF {
    component [Device] as Device
    component [Queue] as Queue
    component [CommandBuffer] as CmdBuf
}

' Main flow
App --> Renderer : BeginFrame()
App --> CmdRec : Record Commands
App --> Renderer : EndFrame()

Renderer --> SwapChain : AcquireNextImage()
Renderer --> CmdPool : Get CommandRecorder
Renderer --> FrameMgr : Synchronize

CmdRec --> RT : BeginRenderPass(target)
CmdRec --> Scene : RenderScene()

Renderer --> Device : Submit Commands
Device --> Queue : Submit to GPU
Queue --> CmdBuf : Execute

SwapChain --> RT : Provides Backbuffer

note top of CmdRec : Core API:\n- Explicit RenderPass\n- nullptr = backbuffer\n- No hidden state

note bottom of FrameMgr : Triple Buffering:\nFrame N: Recording\nFrame N-1: Executing\nFrame N-2: Presenting

@enduml